Subject: Ecommerce Orders


HI Bonnie


Can we please ensure the files for the orders are being sent with the correct purchase order number


Also need to ensure there are no commas in the file otherwise the file will not upload


Below is a list of some of the orders I has to manually look up the correct PO.


This was a very slow and tedious process as I had to go onto every order and look up the customer name in the delivery address field and then I had to search our inbox by the name to locate the email with the correct PO number


There has to be another way we are able to do this without having to go to IT all the time.


Are we able to be supplied a spreadsheet on a weekly bases so we are able to then do a simple VLOOKUP up. Until this issue is resolved


Is there any update with Heath as we were advised he was working on this.
